FOR 	
Reference (18 bytes):

		FOR Marker 				[1]
		Page/Position for loop 	[3]
		Index Variable 			[2] (Integer flag in bit 15)
		Step (+1 optimise) 		[6]
		Terminal Value.	 		[6]

Token list (standard)		
=====================
FOR NEXT DATA INPUT# INPUT DIM READ RESTORE REM ON WAIT LOAD DEF POKE PRINT# CMD SYS OPEN CLOSE GET FN

Token list (X16)
================
MON DOS OLD GEOS VPOKE VLOAD SCREEN PSET LINE FRAME RECT CHAR MOUSE COLOR TEST RESET CLS CODEX LOCATE BOOT KEYMAP 
BLOAD BVLOAD BVERIFY BANK VPEEK MX MY MB JOY 

HEX$ BIN$ (untested)
